    <tr valign="top">
      <td bgcolor="dddddd">\b dal</td>
      <td bgcolor="eeeeee">The <a href="group___d_a_l.html">Data Access Library</a>
      (DAL).</td>
    </tr>
    <tr valign="top">
       <td bgcolor="dddddd">\b cr</td>
    	<td bgcolor="eeeeee">The <a href="group__CR.html">CR-Tools</a> package.
	The configuration script enables selection of the following features from
	the top-level directory: \c CR_WITH_GUI and \c CR_WITH_STARTOOLS - both
	of which are disabled by default. See the page \ref crtools_build_parameters
	for further description.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr valign="top">
      <td bgcolor="dddddd">\b lasa</td>
      <td bgcolor="eeeeee">The <a href="group___l_a_s_a.html">LOFAR Air Shower
      Array</a> (LASA).</td>
    </tr>
    <tr valign="top">
      <td bgcolor="dddddd">\b pulsar</td>
      <td bgcolor="eeeeee">Tools and pipeline developed by the LOFAR Pulsar 
      Working Group.  The majority of the tools are off-the-shelf software
      packages used by the Pulsar community over the last 30 years.  These
